data.text: @MelissaAReed They visited me when I lived in Guatemala City in the 90's. Lived in an apartment with a set up similar to the one seen on Seinfeld. I did not buzz them in. I thought it was hilarious! There's no escape; they're everywhere! Lol 😆
@asthehosptuRNs No they mailed it to me 😬
@MelissaAReed I’ve gotten a few of these before. Haha
@TriageNurseMD @MelissaAReed I got one of these too and found it unsettling that it had my name and address (not just dear neighbor…)!
@MelissaAReed Nothing stops the Jehovah Witnesses. Miss the good old days when my mom would make everyone hide in the kitchen until they left the front porch. Fun times.
@asthehosptuRNs @MelissaAReed We got ours as a mailed letter
@MelissaAReed Did they put it in your door?
@MelissaAReed I got one of those recently. I really did not like that they had my name and address, it really felt invasive
